FW I HATE GOODBYESOriginal Message From Harvey Claudette Sent Wednesday November PM To Dutta Tom Rorschach Reagan Kroll Heather Jafry Rahil Marshall Howard Braddock Billy Acevedo Rudy Piazze Tara Sell Maximilian Emmons Suzette Day Amanda Luong Steven Kelly Mike Laverell Justin Zamora Judy Stewart Jennifer N Bagwell Jennifer J Scheuer Janelle Pagan Ozzie Chapman Christy Chapman Kay Celedon Adriana Subject I HATE GOODBYES Importance High Heres mineplease send yours And you better keep in touch A Thousand Hugs and Kisses Claudette Harvey claude Rolido Dr Houston TX H C

You are cordially invited Cc As you already know Ozzie Pagan is leaving East Power Origination to pursue a position in Enrons Energy Services Not only is he deserting us but he i s stealing Christy Chapman away as well smile Please join me in congratulating them both and wishing them much success in the future To see that they dont forget us too soon lets make his and Christys far ewell a memorable one And what better way to do that than of courseHappy Houryea baby olebmpolebmpolebmp When Friday pm until they throw us out Where Slainte Irish Pub Main St Why Why NOT see ya there claude olebmp olebmp olebmp olebmp olebmp olebmp
